{"title_page": "Mil\u010dice (Mysl\u00edv)", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name                            = \n| subdivision_type2               = [[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n| image_skyline                   = Mil\u010dice, rybn\u00edk III.jpg\n| image_flag                      = \n| image_shield                    = \n| pushpin_map                     = Czech Republic\n| coordinates                     = {{coord|49|24|33|N|13|36|19|E|region:CZ|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type                = Country\n| subdivision_name                = {{CZE}}\n| subdivision_type1               = [[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n| settlement_type                 = Village\n| subdivision_name2               = [[Klatovy District|Klatovy]]\n| subdivision_name1               = [[Plze\u0148 Region|Plze\u0148]]\n| area_total_km2                  = 4.28\n| elevation_m                     = 533\n| population_total                = 98\n| population_as_of                = 2011\n| population_density_km2          = auto\n| postal_code_type                = Postal&nbsp;code\n| postal_code                     = 341 01\n| website                         = http://www.obecmysliv.cz/\n| official_name                   = \n}}\n'''Mil\u010dice''' is a village, part of and located about 2.5&nbsp;km southeast from [[Mysl\u00edv]] in the [[Klatovy District]]. There are 66 addresses registered. \u00a0In 2011, 98 people lived here permanently. It is also a cadastral territory with an area of 4.28&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup>.\n\n== History ==\nThe date of the village's foundation is unknown.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.obecmysliv.cz/cs/historie-a-pamatky-obce-milcice|title=Historie a pam\u00e1tky obce Mil\u010dice {{!}} Obec Mysl\u00edv|website=www.obecmysliv.cz|access-date=2020-01-30}}</ref>\n\n== Chapel of St. Joseph ==\n[[File:Milcice12.jpg|left|thumb]]\n\n== Genealogy and Immigration to America ==\nSo far, about 31 people born in Mil\u010dice have been identified 